{"about_the_game":"<strong>Explore miniature worlds depicting different cultures throughout human history:</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082690/extras/planets_gif_small_02_w576.gif?t=1732243202\" /><br><br><strong>Find characters, objects and stories about our ancestors and learn about their lives:</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082690/extras/NeoFarmerGifSmall.gif?t=1732243202\" /><br><br><strong>Unlock new worlds and progress through time:</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082690/extras/OverviewPlanetUI03SmallAbout.png?t=1732243202\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082690/extras/BookLupeHeaderTextOverviewCentered.png?t=1732243202\" /><br><br>The Human Story is a relaxing, colorful hidden object game in which you explore historically accurate miniature worlds. The game is capturing a big picture view of how human societies and cultures evolved over time from the very first humans in the Old Stone Age until the present day. <br><br>I am a solo dev with a big curiosity for history and creating this game is my way of making sense of the world we are living in today. <br><br><strong>In the first release I am focusing on the Old Stone Age, the New Stone Age and the Bronze Age. Later ages will come with future updates. </strong>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082690/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732243202","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082690/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732243202","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082690/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732243202","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s